07:12.281 --> 07:14.215
have you got some pictures for me

07:14.217 --> 07:15.883
for the <i>el pasaporte?</i>

07:15.885 --> 07:17.685
Uh, yep, I got 'em.

07:17.687 --> 07:19.687
I got water, wine, soda.

07:19.689 --> 07:21.655
Um, I'm good. Thanks.

07:21.657 --> 07:23.457
I'm sorry, is my penis bothering you?

07:23.459 --> 07:24.892
Not if it keeps its distance.

07:24.894 --> 07:26.627
Well, now it's bothering me, so...

07:26.629 --> 07:28.796
I keep forgetting that
not everybody's used to

07:28.798 --> 07:30.765
this Neighborhood living.

07:30.767 --> 07:32.566
All right, let's see 'em.

07:32.568 --> 07:34.301
Oh, nice. Good.

07:34.303 --> 07:36.070
Yeah, nice. Flat.

07:36.072 --> 07:37.638
Yeah, well done.

07:37.640 --> 07:39.707
- I can work with this.
- Okay, great, yeah.

07:39.709 --> 07:41.375
Um, my friends and I...

07:41.377 --> 07:43.644
I don't know if Esme told you,
but we got robbed.

07:43.646 --> 07:44.845
