We went to the consulate...

07:44.847 --> 07:46.046
No, no, no, no, no.

07:46.048 --> 07:49.016
You don't ask me questions.
I don't ask you questions.

07:49.018 --> 07:49.817
We just do business.

07:49.819 --> 07:51.886
It's all wonderfully wonderful.

07:51.888 --> 07:53.654
- Okay, great.
- It is great.

07:53.656 --> 07:56.357
'Cause you are gonna bring me
the rest of the money next week,

07:56.359 --> 07:58.926
and I'll have these
passports ready for you, huh?

07:58.928 --> 08:00.227
Ain't life grand?

08:00.229 --> 08:02.163
