09:48.170 --> 09:49.970
Damn.

09:51.007 --> 09:54.541
- I don't believe this!
- Oh, come on.

09:54.543 --> 09:56.343
You should be happy for him.
He's finally getting laid.

09:56.345 --> 09:58.712
No, this is a total betrayal
of the ex code, okay?

09:58.714 --> 10:00.347
And we're the sidekicks,

10:00.349 --> 10:02.449
