13:39.707 --> 13:41.673
Well, Mother's looking for you.

13:41.675 --> 13:43.275
There's a first for everything.

13:43.277 --> 13:44.510
The least you could do is
show up to your own party.

13:44.512 --> 13:45.911
I didn't ask for a party.

13:45.913 --> 13:48.614
No, you did something far more gauche.

13:48.616 --> 13:50.215
You graduated from art school,

13:50.217 --> 13:54.086
which apparently is cause
for celebration, so...

13:54.088 --> 13:55.454
let's celebrate.

13:55.456 --> 13:57.189
Maybe I don't feel like celebrating.

13:57.191 --> 13:59.358
Maybe I feel like I
did something shitty.

13:59.360 --> 14:01.794
- You're being emotional.
- Because I have emotions!

14:01.796 --> 14:04.263
- Well, they're unbecoming.
- You're a goblin.

14:04.265 --> 14:05.499
Get out.

14:06.600 --> 14:08.367
